22#include <sys/cdefs.h>
23#ifndef lint
24__RCSID("$NetBSD: print-raw.c,v 1.6 2017/02/05 04:05:05 spz Exp $");
25#endif
26
27/* \summary: Raw IP printer */
28
29#ifdef HAVE_CONFIG_H
30#include "config.h"
31#endif
32
33#include <netdissect-stdinc.h>
34
35#include "netdissect.h"
36
37/*
38 * The DLT_RAW packet has no header. It contains a raw IP packet.
39 */
40
41u_int
42raw_if_print(netdissect_options *ndo, const struct pcap_pkthdr *h, const u_char *p)
43{
44 if (ndo->ndo_eflag)
45 ND_PRINT((ndo, "ip: "));
46
47 ipN_print(ndo, p, h->len);
48
49 return (0);
50}
